The ">" (&gt;) in the Breadcrumbs are partly hardcoded. Many of them can be changed by updating tons of templates, but one is hardcoded in com.atlassian.confluence.pages.actions.AbstractPageAction - I cannot change that.
A centralized option for that would be great. I'd like to have an image instead of ">"...

If you change  
{dynamicTaskList:upgradeSteps}

to 

{dynamicTaskList:Steps to Upgrade}

all tasks are lost.

Would be nice if some other identifier could be used internally to keep the tasks present on a change of task list title.

